FeedLike.name: FeedLike
FeedLike.description: Indicates that a user has liked a feed item.

FeedItemId.description: ID of the feed item that the user liked.

FeedEntityId.description: The ID of a feed item or feed comment the user liked. If the user liked a comment, FeedEntityId is set to the ID of the comment. If the user liked a feed item, FeedEntityId is set to the ID of the feed item. This field is optional. The default value is the ID of the feed item.

InsertedById.description: ID of the user who added this item to the feed. For example, if an application migrates posts and comments from another application into a feed, the InsertedBy value is set to the ID of the context user.
